<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>You have to wait for Grofflah, once you give him the note<BR>
that you got from Alayel, he will "decode" it for you, and<BR>
return it in a form that you can read.<BR>
<BR>
He spawns in the part of the bar where the bards are<BR>
standing around.<BR>
<BR>
The beggar spawns in the same part of the bar, but he<BR>
spawns next to the bar counter.<BR>
<BR>
Niko</font></td></tr></table>
